# QC shim (baseline): base + transform ONLY, no horizon. Reasoned separately so the invariant
# check can prove the horizon layer adds NO new entailment about any base/transform term.
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
<https://w3id.org/rockworx/horizon-qc/baseline> a owl:Ontology ;
    owl:imports <https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq>,
        <https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/transform> .
